                    "author": "soontobemrscool",
                    "score": 13,
                    "body": "And let’s not act like the billionaire scum didn’t get exactly what he wanted. All the “ she was a gold digger “ comments, so? She fulfilled her end of the bargain. If it wasn’t her it would have been someone else.",
                    "replies": [
                      {
                        "id": "n9qa33l",
