                    "author": "profanedivinity",
                    "score": 7,
                    "body": "Thanks for this insight. And agreed. A real dick move to not be as transparent as possible with such an impossibly large nest egg.\n\nThe dude was 89 and was acting like a 6 year old hiding a vase that he broke. Tells you a lot about how emotionally immature and insufferable this person must have been, it must have been extremely stressful for Anna Nichole Smith.",
                    "replies": []
