            "author": "DefinitelyN0tAM0th",
            "score": 82,
            "body": "There’s a really interesting You’re Wrong About episode on this \n\nThis particular billionaire had a thing for gold diggers, and one of his previous wives died getting a enhancement surgery of some sort like a facelift or something like that that went horribly wrong \n\nHe proposed to Anna Nichole multiple times and she turned him down constantly because she wanted to make sure that she could fulfill her dreams first and foremost. So she became a model and a successful model at that before she consented to marrying him, and she largely married him because he was a really positive support system for her coming from a situation where she was a single mother working as a sex worker and just basically struggling and being treated shit shitty by other people. \n\nAm I gonna sit here and tell you that she was in love with him? No. But he made her feel safe, and he respected her wishes, and he continued to pursue her in a non-aggressive manner until she on her own terms agreed to be with him they seem to actually really get along.",
